I  got this game today, give a try another Zombie survival game, Got a shock, you can turn off Zombies and spend your time collecting wood,stone and bits and just build a base until ready to take on zombies,
For a reasonably cheap game its very good, infact it reminds me a lot of RUST at very start until it started to add stupid things.
if you like to build this game is for you,
